    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to FREEFLOW.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/e72cdd96a0c0ba8ff3880d62f3a9eb3e.poster.avif?t=1766860970\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/e72cdd96a0c0ba8ff3880d62f3a9eb3e.webm?t=1766860970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/e72cdd96a0c0ba8ff3880d62f3a9eb3e.mp4?t=1766860970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >FREEFLOW brings fun and smooth movement, highly inspired by KARLSON, set in a mysterious, facility. Parkour your way out of the facility with your grappling gun and skills, and figure out the dark secret to this evil facility...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/44ae3f754c66542b9495e35963d1b508.poster.avif?t=1766860970\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/44ae3f754c66542b9495e35963d1b508.webm?t=1766860970\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306800/extras/44ae3f754c66542b9495e35963d1b508.mp4?t=1766860970\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game's parkour system lets you move at very quick speeds and swing with your unique grappling gun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a test subject in a dark facility, made to test parkour abilities. When you wake up, you are greeted with a Artificial Voice explaining what you have to do to progress. As you make your way through the facility, you slowly figure out that there is something wrong with this place. There is a unknown evil to this facility, can you discover it?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Current Gameplay Features:</u></i> <br>Singleplayer &quot;Story&quot; Mode (in progress)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Main Levels and 1 Secret Level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Movement Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grappling Gun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more to come!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Credits:</strong></u><br><br>Benjib20YT - Game Developer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shozzakai - Voice Actor, Story Board, Vent Boy</p>",
